	<div style="text-align:right;">
		GUSATTO, Francine<sup>1</sup>; GIBBERT, Patrícia<sup>2</sup>; BORTOLINI, Michele Fernanda<sup>3</sup>		<BR>
		PIBITI		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBITI		<BR>
